query:
select
                    n.id as from_id,
                    e.to_node_id to_id,
                    n.data as "from_data?: _",
                    n.type as from_type,
                    n.key as from_key,
                    n.name as from_name,
                    n2.name as to_name,
                    e.condition as "condition?: _",
                    n.workflow_id,
                    el.output as "from_output?: _",
                    el.id as "execution_log_id?: _"
                from
                    node n
                join edge e on
                    n.id = e.from_node_id
                join node n2 on
                    e.to_node_id = n2.id
                left join execution_log el on
                    n.id = el.node_id
                    and el.execution_id = $1
                where
                    n.workflow_id = $2
